        "title": "Answer",
        "style": null,
        "decorator": null,
        "content": "<p>A part of supply chain management, inventory management (or stock management) is the process of managing a business&#39; inventory and stock. To further define inventory management, we can note that it includes aspects like the storage of inventory, overseeing orders for stock inventory, and controlling the number of items in stock.&nbsp;</p>\n",
